Phono-semantic compound ( 形聲 / 形声 , OC *luɡ ): phonetic 𡍬 ( OC *mluɡ ) + semantic 貝 ; the original version is 𧸇 . 𡍬 was further reduced to 士 and 四 to give its present form, which is often confused with the graphically (and semantically) similar but etymologically unrelated 賣 .
